# React Flow -- Complete API Reference

> Package: `@xyflow/react`. FREE version only. All imports are named exports.

## ReactFlow Component Props

```tsx
import { ReactFlow } from "@xyflow/react";
```

### Core Props

| Prop                 | Type                 | Default | Description                          |
| -------------------- | -------------------- | ------- | ------------------------------------ |
| `nodes`              | `Node[]`             | `[]`    | Array of node objects                |
| `edges`              | `Edge[]`             | `[]`    | Array of edge objects                |
| `defaultNodes`       | `Node[]`             | -       | Initial nodes for uncontrolled mode  |
| `defaultEdges`       | `Edge[]`             | -       | Initial edges for uncontrolled mode  |
| `onNodesChange`      | `OnNodesChange`      | -       | Called when nodes change             |
| `onEdgesChange`      | `OnEdgesChange`      | -       | Called when edges change             |
| `onConnect`          | `OnConnect`          | -       | Called when a new connection is made |
| `nodeTypes`          | `NodeTypes`          | -       | Custom node component registry       |
| `edgeTypes`          | `EdgeTypes`          | -       | Custom edge component registry       |
| `defaultEdgeOptions` | `DefaultEdgeOptions` | -       | Defaults applied to new edges        |

### Components

- **Background**: `<Background variant={BackgroundVariant.Dots} gap={16} size={1} />`
- **Controls**: `<Controls showZoom showFitView showInteractive />`
- **MiniMap**: `<MiniMap pannable zoomable />`
- **Panel**: `<Panel position="top-left">...</Panel>`
- **Handle**: `<Handle type="source" position={Position.Right} />`
- **NodeToolbar**: `<NodeToolbar isVisible={selected} position={Position.Top}>...</NodeToolbar>`
- **NodeResizer**: `<NodeResizer minWidth={100} minHeight={30} isVisible={selected} />`
- **EdgeLabelRenderer**: Renders edge labels in the DOM (not SVG)
- **ViewportPortal**: Renders elements in the viewport coordinate system

